    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，配置策略是起点。策略配好后，Azure Backup Vault要主动去触发Workload VM上的快照任务，这个用虚线箭头表示异步触发比较合适。然后Workload VM完成备份后，要把恢复点信息回传给Azure Backup Vault。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Workload VM",
        "Trigger snapshot/backup job",
        "Send recovery point"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把前三个交互画出来了：ClinEng到Azure的实线箭头标注Configure policy，Azure到Workload的虚线箭头标注Trigger snapshot/backup job，Workload返回Azure的虚线箭头标注Send recovery point。最后一步是Clinical Engineer验证恢复点和报告吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Configure policy",
