    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成，四条消息流都加上了。标题我定为Module 16 – Backup Alerts and Monitoring (Education_LMS_Portal)，参与者别名设置ClinEng、Azure、Workload，显示名称保留全称。整个流程闭环了：配置→触发→回传→验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
